name: idiVD
comment:
Virtual deduction proof of ~ idiALT . The following user's proof is completed by invoking mmj2's unify command and using mmj2's StepSelector to pick all remaining steps of the Metamath proof.
h1:: ` |- ph `
qed:1,?: ~ e0a ` |- ph `
